  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT288-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṉatu varavuṇarntu “nam perumāṉ namakku aṉpilar” eṉṟa tōḻikkuk
          kiḻatti uraittatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Told by HER to the confidante who said “our great man is
          without love [for us]!”, after having realised HIS coming. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT288">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> kaṟivaḷa raṭukkat tāṅkaṇ muṟiyaruntu</l>
          <l> kuraṅkoruṅ kirukkum peruṅka ṉāṭa</l>
          <l> ṉiṉiya ṉākali ṉiṉatti ṉiyaṉṟa</l>
          <l> viṉṉā maiyiṉu miṉitō</l>
          <l> viṉiteṉap paṭūum puttē ṇāṭē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>The land of the gods is called pleasing.</l>
          <l>Is it more pleasing than the unpleasantness</l>
          <l rend="indent">which came from the family , because he is pleasing,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">the man from a land of big stones, where monkeys are together</l>
          <l rend="indent3">[and] eat from the shoots at the mountain side</l>
          <l rend="indent8">where pepper grows?</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
